# .husky/commit-msg
# Location: .husky/commit-msg
#
# WHY pnpm exec instead of npx?
# We chose pnpm as our package manager. "pnpm exec" runs a binary
# that is already installed in node_modules — no downloading needed.
# "npx --no --" was npm-specific syntax. pnpm exec is the pnpm equivalent.
pnpm exec commitlint --edit $1
